===Adjective===
{{en-ad2|'''quiet'''|'''[[quieter]]'''|'''[[quietest]]'''}}
# With little or no sound; [[denote|denoting]] [[absence]] of [[disturb]]ing [[noise]].
# Absence of significant [[motion]] or [[activity]]; [[calm]] (''the sea was quiet; a quiet night at home;all quiet on the Western [[front]].'')
# Low [[quantity]]; ''(the [[traffic]] was quiet for a Monday morning; [[business]] was quiet for the season.'')
# The [[human]] [[attribute]] of not [[talk]]ing much; or of not talking [[loud]]ly.

